Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{Nothing you need to subtitle. It's for Heart Kruez (SP?), the Fairy Tail world's womans accessory company. Erza forces them to make her armor for her}{is there some significance to the "HK" on her suitcase?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make sure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like the client really appreciated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we finished it up real quick since I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? And what makes you say that, jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:28.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about how you were nothing but extra baggage for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:31.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I teach you what kind of extra baggage I am? {This line isn't supposed to make sense, so Gray can tell him it doesn't make sense in the next line}{going a bit non-literal here, to keep Natsu not getting the metaphorical meaning of "baggage"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That made no sense at all. {in response to the above line}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And put on some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Upa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who says that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:51.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:57.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:02.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:06.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:13.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:20.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:25.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:33.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:39.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:42.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:50.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:02:01.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I hate to interrupt your conversation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who chose this request on my own, originally...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did everyone come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:24.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we're Fairy Tail's strongest team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put together me, Happy, Erza, and underpants-man, and there's no job we can't do! {I like "underpants-man"} {Just "underpants" alone seems odd in english, hence I'm adding the "man"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me underpants-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it gives me reassurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:46.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgetting someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're kiddin', sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Oopy! {Naw, Oopy's fine. I might have used Oovy instead, but since Levy plays such a role here, I'd rather not go with the "v" in this episode}{wow, natsu doesn't even get the name close... "u-bi-"... Maybe another spelling would be better... You have a better sense of "Fairy Tail" name style, so feel free to change this}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying, and I'm not named "Oopy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was carried away. And I have ended up hurting my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow this to continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, would you please punch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the punch-line I had in mind... {I love it for manga or dub. I wonder how well the sub fans would go for it. It'd be perfect for manga, where you can have a note at the end telling people just how close to the Japanese this actually is, but without that, it might be taken as the hard-core fan's high crime of localizing the humor. Still, it's close enough for me to not touch it.}{how about this "translation?" I think it works great!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fairy Tail wizards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor things...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're drawing an unusual amount of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? The guild shouldn't look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:07.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but they got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fairy Tail's first basement floor. {There was an English sign in Vol. 6 for this scene that just said, "Fairy Tail Basement" since I think this Fairy Tail building had only one basement floor. I think the next guild building has two basement floors}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's normally used for storage, but it's been turned into a temporary beer hall. {Not thinking of anything better.}{better word for sakaba? Bar seems off...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've always been on bad terms with Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against Phantom... {\i1}That{\i0} Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, what're you sittin' around here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The job go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, don't you understand the situation we're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild's been busted up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something to get so riled up about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:04:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:06.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom? That's all those half-wits got in 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking the guild when nobody was here? Who'd take pleasure in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:11.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:15.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the attack happened in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why no one is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's one small thing to be thankful for. {every cloud has a silver lining doesn't really work here}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can only manage a sneak-attack, we shouldn't even give those bastards the time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't worth our time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't {\i1}right{\i0}, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be satisfied until we go and crush these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This discussion is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the upstairs is repaired, we'll take work requests from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't time for doing jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:41.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had about enough out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you spank {\i1}me{\i0}, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'll get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta pee. {I like this line}{or a bit more literal and obfuscated "overflowin' here..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you okay with this, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just as hard for the master, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But outright conflict between guilds is forbidden by the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're the ones that attacked first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:17.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how the master feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:28.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have really gotten complicated, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Missy! Don't blame me if you fall in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:38.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom is famous for not getting along with Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually fretted trying to decide which one I wanted to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, their reputation is nearly as nuts as Fairy Tail's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I made the right decision joining here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Fairy Tail is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whassap?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice room you have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the best?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with Phantom means that they've come to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:09.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible they've looked up where everyone lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll be safer if we stay in groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Mira-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is having sleepovers here and there today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a girl of a certain age,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and even I would be a bit uncomfortable staying with just Natsu and Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have decided to keep you all company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not here to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Natsu and Gray staying with me was already decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her laundry! {for a second there, I thought the joke was that Happy and Natsu brought over their laundry for Lucy to do}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cat over there, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Plue, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Plue! What's that you're eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:51.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, look! I found some sexy underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You actually wear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hittin' the hay so pipe down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're enjoying the change of pace in someone else's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... You all smell like sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sleeping in the same room, so at least take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna! What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sleeepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I must. Shall we take a bath together like we used to long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of relationship do you guys have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Strongest Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the kind of strength it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about this, Levy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better for you to stay with Laki at the girl's dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to fear with the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Natsu... You can use it next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:05.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, even... They've all made themselves way too much at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong with this, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You even requip to change clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Phantom suddenly attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had a lot of smaller skirmishes before this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but never such a direct attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Gramps weren't such a scardey-cat we could just destroy the punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:37.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps isn't scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the Ten Wizard Saints, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're reading so nonchalantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I wanna know what happens next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Levy-chan is going to be my first reader. It's already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's that hand for, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you mentioned Ten Wizard Saints?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:04.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a title bestowed by the Chairman of the Magic Council to the greatest ten wizards on the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master of Phantom, Jose, is also one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:15.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His {\i1}is{\i0} scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing Phantom's got are numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master and Mira-chan want to avoid a fight because they know the consequences of two guilds battling each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to help preserve the peace of the entire world of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Phantom really that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:42.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys ain't nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... If it came to blows, mutual destruction is ensured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our offensive powers are about equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Makarov is said to be on par with Master Jose, also one of the ten wizard saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there are the Element 4, their S-class level wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our biggest worry is "Iron" Gajeel. {I used the Japanese word Kurogane in the manga, but I have no objections to "iron." But although he's a dragon slayer, I don't think "Iron Dragon" was intended as his nickname.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:09.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one I believe is responsible for the attack on the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are ones other than Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean he like... eats iron and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you attacked Fairy Tail, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:32.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're all feelin' really blue right about now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves 'em right, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:44.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you before. Don't talk to me when I'm eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about those Fairy Butts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're more powerful than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The seed has been sown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, Gajeel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast, Master. {Gajeel's way of speaking should be a reflection on Natsu's. He's basically Dark Natsu. So try to keep is dialog as unintellectual as you can.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That trash won't act from just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I left them an extra little present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure to keep that one alive, please. {He's referring to Lucy. He doesn't care of the rest are murdered.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnolia Southgate Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're from the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody get them down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better steer clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet! Droy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stand being reduced to a run-down beer hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But no parent can stand idle while the blood of his children is spilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To war!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnolia Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:33.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are also equipped with facilities to treat wizards. {in this case nyuuin means they can the whole hospital treatment, not just admitting}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:46.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could Phantom do this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super curious, Lu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you're writing a novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor's already made the rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a good idea who it was that spread it around...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I never properly introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy McGarden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this here's Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Droy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Team Shadow Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm hopeless at writing, but I love reading books!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, would you let me read your book?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:31.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... It's not something I'd want to show other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the point of writing to let other people read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that being an author is like showing off your butt to everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get anywhere being embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not talking about your butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be fine, too, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still working on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when it's finished, can I be the first person to read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And she worked so hard for us back then... {wow, actually acknowledging that episode's existence?....}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oak Town, in the North-East of the Kingdom of Fiore. {Yikes, the English caption on-screen had "town" and you had "city"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:36.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the center, towering above the old castle town, is a branch of the Phantom Lord guild. {There was an unfortunate line break between castle and town, so when I read it, it the idea of a castle being still in the town was stuck in my head. In this case, I think the castle has been replaced by the guild building.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Fairy Butts are all busted up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:47.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear that Gajeel went and did in three more of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go do some work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:16:00.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And on our way back, we'll pluck off a few Fairy wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who... Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish them off! {amusing this for him to say...}{Who? The script just says Fairy Tail Member. Is it Nab or Reedus?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Purple Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spark Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice shot, Bisca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting rusty, Al! {abbreviation for Alzack}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Target Lock On!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Homing Shot! {"Shot" works great for me}{would you prefer Shoot, despite grammar ickiness? normally I'd keep shoot (like in shugo chara, the "Golden Victory Shoot") but here "homing shot" is such standard english I'll use that}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You laid hands on this monster's children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think any human laws will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the rank-and-file ain't bad either! {Yup. I used "troops" in the manga} {I presume by "heitai" they mean like, "rank and file"...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are Fairy Tail wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pict Magic! {Pict Magic}{fix this to how you usually spell it}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature, run wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Make:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dam of Shy Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that supposed to mean? {no kidding...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, someone we can beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...wizard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I'm a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Gajeel and the Element 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Titania Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus and Mystogan are sitting things out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocky bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:23.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But things are going pretty much according to Master Jose's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They rage pretty good for trash... {my attempt}{hmm, don't like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:38.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan and her team need someone to care for them, so I guess that's me. {too many "someone"s}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! A sunshower?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop. {I went more literal in the manga to "gentle and steady." Yours works, I think}{this is not particularly literal. "shinshinto" is technically the sound of rain or snow falling silently. However I think her performance implies the gentleness. Taken from lyrics to one of my favorite disney songs, and matches the diction perfectly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is the rain-woman. {Yup. I had that too. Although I didn't worry about "a" vs. "the." It doesn't come up all that often.}{Juvia will rever to herself in the third person in English as well.  Furthermore, she is "the" rain-woman, not "a" rain-woman... I see that as part of her self-loathing.  P.S. about 2 weeks ago when the last arc ended I went and read the Japanese manga all the way through volume 12, so I am familiar with what goes on through the tower of heaven and loke arcs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:59.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pleasure. Fare thee well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non, non, non, non, non!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With non of 3, 3, 7, I say to you, bonjour!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's another weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia-sama, you mustn't abandon your job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My monocle, it whispers to me, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It tells me that this mademoiselle is our beloved cible. {note: cible is french for "target"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:35.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it was this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:37.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Target?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize for the late introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:44.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sol, one of the Element 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me Sol of the Land... Please call me Monsieur Sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Element 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We two have come to collect you for the great Phantom Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:03.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the rain-woman of the Element 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People call her Juvia of the Deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do such a thing to Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With non of 3, I correct your error!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying your guild and attacking Levy-sama was all the work of Gajeel-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:28.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is true that all of us in the guild were for the idea, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:36.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's water lock cannot be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Très bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fear. Juvia will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it is Juvia's job to bring back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Lucy Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Victoire! {note: means, duh, victory}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have captured the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how 'bout some of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've eaten, I'm all revved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be? He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:34.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Make: The Distance Between the Two is Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:37.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, no clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns Magic! Mad Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip! Magic Shotgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wide Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, droopy eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good yourself, squinty eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:54.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:56.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest here to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose is likely on the top floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put him out of commission for good... {I made a dark joke out of it (which I'm pretty proud of), but it's a little too long for this subtitle. I don't mind this translation.}{maybe this is a bit too whitewashed...  the meaning is much harsher than this, but I don't think Makarov would say "kill him" even in anger}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the biggest threat's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I should mix it up a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:40.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:52.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:57.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:03.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:10.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:21.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:30.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:34.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:37.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:41.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:54.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:59.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! We forgot to take Lucy with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:03.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be angry that we left her behind this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's real scary when she's angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:08.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring her something back as a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think she'd rather we pay her rent for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Lucy Heartfilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I just heard Lucy's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.71,0:24:20.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're hounding her about the rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:22.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-That can't be it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
